## Theory ##

A package is a physical folder structure that contains group of classes,
interfaces or sub-packages.

## Advantages ##

1)Well organized.
2)Increases readability.
3)Access control: Visibility control
4)Reusability : Common code can be used by making common folder can be reuse by everyone

## Types of packages ##
1)Build-in package : The package that is already defined is called build-in package.
2)User-defined package : The package that is created by user is called user-defined package.

## Visbility ##

public > protected > default > private